><td>-0.76</td></tr><tr><td>晶門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02878:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02878-HK</a>)</td><td>0.53</td><td>-1.85</td></tr><tr><td>宏光半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06908:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06908\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06908-HK</a>)</td><td>0.61</td><td>-1.61</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
